SUMMARY:MTG Marvel: Super Heroes Draft @ Top Deck Games - Cherry Hill
LOCATION:Top Deck Games - Cherry Hill\, 1400 Haddonfield-Berlin Road\, Che
 rry Hill Township\, New Jersey\, 08003
DESCRIPTION:Format: Draft\nCost: $30\nStore: https://www.topdeckgamesonlin
 e.com/\nDetails: https://locator.wizards.com/events/10952190\n\nThe multiv
 erse is under threat—and this time\, it’s calling in the heroes.\nStep
  into the action with Magic: The Gathering – Marvel: Super Heroes and un
 leash powers beyond imagination at our prerelease event! Suit up alongside
  legendary icons\, clash with unstoppable villains\, and forge your own he
 roic legacy with every draw. Whether you’re assembling your dream team o
 r going solo to save the day\, this is your moment to rise.\nThe battle st
 arts now—are you ready to answer the call?\n\nWHEN: Sunday\, June 21st\,
  3:00pm\n\nWHERE: Top Deck Games\n1400 Haddonfield-Berlin Rd\, Suite 100\n
 Cherry Hill\, NJ 08003\n856-858-2700\n\nENTRY: $30\n- Players must have an
  active Wizards Account / MTG Companion App Account\n- Sign up for an acco
 unt at https://myaccounts.wizards.com/register\n\nFORMAT: Booster Draft\n-
  3x Play Boosters\n- 3 Swiss Rounds\, Best of 3\n- 50 minute Rounds\n\nPRI
 ZES: Store Credit based on final record\n3-0-0: $40\n2-0-1: $30\n2-1-0: $2
 0\n1-1-1: $10\nSource: wizards-locator
URL;VALUE=URI:https://locator.wizards.com/events/10952190
END:VEVENT
